Steps of VM part: 
Step 1: create Linux vm

Step 2: install a apache2 in your server 

Step 3: create connection between vm and file share these steps are in folder "creating-mount-storage-linux.txt"

Step 4: after the connection you need move file /mnt/azure path to var/www/html path

Step 5: after successfully moved means hit VM IP in browser application will host

Steps Storage account part:
Step 1: create one storage account 

Step 2: connect the storage account to Azure storage explorer

Step 3: create file share in your storage account

Step 4: Upload your application file in fileshre

